Package: aks-flex-node
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, systemd, curl, jq
Recommends: docker.io | containerd
Suggests: kubectl
Description: AKS Flex Node Agent
 The AKS Flex Node Agent automates the deployment, configuration,
 and management of Azure Kubernetes Service (AKS) edge nodes.
 .
 Key features:
  - Automated node bootstrap and configuration
  - Azure Arc integration
  - Health monitoring and self-healing
  - Kubernetes component management
  - Systemd service integration
 .
 This package provides a systemd service that can be installed via
 apt and managed like any other system service.